\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Bio: I am a graduate of Ringling College of Art and Design (class of 2013), and previously worked in the video game industry as a generalist (painting/sculpting/programming/design). I left the industry to pursue personal projects. Invincible Dread is one of these.}}